Hello!

While not much of a new member to this team(I've been contributing for about a month now) I'm still pretty new when it comes to writing code in Rust. I'm a member of the Triage working group - we may have met already if I annoyed you about progress on a PR or labeled your issue.

I plan to stick around for a while and do a lot of small things here and there!
Thank you for your work! The triage working group is incredibly valuable.
